sday Gutierrez</strong>. Former digital marketing manager for the London 2012 Festival, the largest UK festival ever staged. This is her blog about contemporary art, design, film, photography and all that move her soul.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/woody-allens-midnight-in-paris-and-the-roaring-twenties/","prev":{"id":"da9c894e-74c7-55f2-9cf0-bef4de78e768","fields":{"slug":"/project-2012-artists-come-together-for-the-end-of-the/","prefix":"2011-10-25","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Project 2012: Artists Come Together for the End of the World","category":"interviews"}},"next":{"id":"a6b4c52d-0312-59dc-b35f-49dfe69bcfb8","fields":{"slug":"/miracles-and-charms-infinitas-gracias-at-the-wellcome-trust/","prefix":"2011-11-19","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Miracles and Charms: Infinitas Gracias at the Wellcome Trust","category":"exhibits"}},"source":"posts"}}